name: Albert Wesker [Resident Evil] Mini Dude #130
description: Dr. Albert Wesker (アルバート・ウェスカー) was an accomplished virologist notorious for his work with groups affiliated with the bio-weapons black market. Originally one of the test subjects in Project W who specialised in biotechnology and bioengineering, Wesker was an elite perfectionist individual of absolute coldness, always wearing deep-black sunglasses that gave him an even more unapproachable air.
